Interface UserInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelObserver, java.util.Observer
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface UserInterface
extends ModelObserver

    An interface for user interface used with Chessly By FrankKopp. The interface has currently no fields or methods but extends the java.util.Observer via the ModelObserver interface.
